'''BIGBANG'''（{{lang-ko|'''빅뱅'''}}；{{lang-ja|'''ビッグバン'''}}）是[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]於2006年推出的[[韓國|韓國]][[男子組合|男子組合]]，最初由[[T.O.P.|T.O.P]]、[[太陽_(歌手)|太陽]]、[[G-Dragon|G-Dragon]]、[[姜大聲|姜大聲]]<ref>{{cite news |language =  | author =  | url = http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/Kang_Dae_Sung_Chinese_Signature.jpg | title = 姜大聲本人的中文簽名為大聲。 | publisher = Mnet wide | pages =  | date =2008-07-20 | accessdate =2012-07-29}}</ref>以及[[勝利_(歌手)|勝利]]五位成員組成。G-Dragon擔任隊長一職，他們的團體名稱「BIGBANG」為宇宙大爆炸之意（The Big Bang Theory），意味著將對於韓國音樂界，甚至在全世界帶來爆炸性的影響。官方的歌迷名稱則是「V.I.P」，其意思為「Very Important Person」，是根據第二張單曲《[[BIGBANG_Is_V.I.P|BIGBANG Is V.I.P]]》命名，有著粉絲是非常重要的人的含意。官方應援物為黃色皇冠造型手燈。

==簡介==
團體剛出道時主要以嘻哈曲風為重，首張[[BIGBANG_(2006年單曲)|同名專輯]]賣出近4萬張<ref name="2007年專輯銷售量">{{cite web |url=http://www.yg-life.com/archives/79246?lang=en#qtranslate-2-chooser |title=[Entertainment History] Looking Back on the Past 10 Years of BIGBANG, Who Transformed From Teenagers to Global Stars |publisher=yg-life |date=2016-08-19 |accessdate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，成果尚未顯著，直至2007年發行第一張迷你專輯《[[Always_(BIGBANG迷你專輯)|Always]]》時一舉成名，令組合打響知名度的歌曲〈{{link-en|謊言 (BIGBANG歌曲)|Lies (Big Bang song)|謊言}}〉便收錄於此張專輯中，此曲在韓國各大音樂榜單中破紀錄的蟬聯了七週的冠軍<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title=[NEWS] Big Bang's "Lies" lingered in Melon chart for 54 weeks! |url=http://www.dkpopnews.net/2011/02/news-big-bangs-lies-lingered-in-melon.html |website=dkpopnews |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.dkpopnews.net/2011/02/news-big-bangs-lies-lingered-in-melon.html |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，並使BIGBANG在第9屆「[[Mnet亞洲音樂大獎|Mnet亞洲音樂大獎]]」榮獲首座年度歌曲大獎<ref>{{cite web|title=VIP們，你是何時喜歡BIGBANG的呢？ |url=http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/76860 |website=韓星網 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/76860 |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>。BIGBANG後續發行的唱片也為他們提高了知名度，而帶動BIGBANG踏上世界的舞臺是在2012年推出的第五張韓語迷你專輯《{{link-en|Alive (BIGBANG迷你專輯)|Alive (EP)|Alive}}》，這張專輯發行後成為第一張登上[[美國|美國]][[公告牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]的韓國專輯<ref name="告示牌200大專輯榜">{{cite web|title=Big Bang's 'Alive' charts on the Billboard 200 |url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/03/big-bangs-alive-charts-on-the-billboard-200 |website=allkpop |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/03/big-bangs-alive-charts-on-the-billboard-200 |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=BILLBOARD 200 |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/billboard-200/2012-03-17 |website=告示牌 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.billboard.com/charts/billboard-200/2012-03-17 |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，並獲得海外媒體的關注，包括在該年登上美國[[格萊美|格萊美]]官方網頁，成為第一個被格萊美介紹的韓國歌手<ref name="BigBang登美國格萊美網站首頁 K-POP熱潮令人嘆為觀止">{{cite web |title=BigBang登美國格萊美網站首頁 K-POP熱潮令人嘆為觀止 |url=http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/16011 |website=韓星網 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120418000808/http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/16011 |archivedate=2012-04-18 }}</ref>。其後發行的《[[M_(BIGBANG單曲)|M]]》、《[[A_(BIGBANG單曲)|A]]》、《[[D_(BIGBANG單曲)|D]]》、《[[E_(BIGBANG單曲)|E]]》及在2016年推出的該系列結尾作《[[MADE_(BIGBANG專輯)|MADE]]》則奠定了BIGBANG在[[韓國流行音樂|韓國流行音樂]]上的地位，同時於發行後均取得商業上的成功，僅是「Made Series」系列單曲的部分在亞洲的淨銷售就超過了1300萬張<ref name=":9">{{cite web|title=Big Bang's Album Sales, World Tour Earn Them A Cool $128 Million In 2015 |url=http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/262984/20151215/big-bang-2015.htm |website=kpopstarz |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/262984/20151215/big-bang-2015.htm |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，並讓團體第三次在「Mnet亞洲音樂大獎」上獲頒年度歌手獎。<ref>{{cite web|title=MAMA／（有片）EXO、BIGBANG橫掃大獎 並列4冠王！ |url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1527643 |website=自由時報 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1527643 |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>

BIGBANG在數年來不斷的自我突破、刷新韓國流行音樂多項紀錄，被國際譽為「K-POP流行音樂之王」、「韓國國民男團」<ref>{{cite web|title=Review: Kings of K-Pop BIGBANG Performs First U.S. Show In 3 Years |url=http://www.vibe.com/2015/10/review-big-bang-performs-first-us-show-in-3-years/ |website=vibe |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.vibe.com/2015/10/review-big-bang-performs-first-us-show-in-3-years/ |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=BigBang is going on tour: Get to know the kings of K-Pop |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/bigbang-is-going-on-tour-get-to-know-the-kings-of-k-pop |website=straitstimes |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/bigbang-is-going-on-tour-get-to-know-the-kings-of-k-pop |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=K-Pop Kings BIGBANG Fly Seoul’s Soul to NYC |url=https://www.villagevoice.com/2015/10/12/k-pop-kings-bigbang-fly-seouls-soul-to-nyc/ |website=villagevoice |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/https://www.villagevoice.com/2015/10/12/k-pop-kings-bigbang-fly-seouls-soul-to-nyc/ |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=BIGBANG: The biggest boy band in the world you probably haven’t heard of |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2016/04/21/bigbang-biggest-boy-band-world-you-probably-havent-heard/83197506/ |website=usatoday |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2016/04/21/bigbang-biggest-boy-band-world-you-probably-havent-heard/83197506/ |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang - The kings of kpop are back |url=http://uk.blastingnews.com/showbiz-tv/2015/04/big-bang-the-kings-of-kpop-are-back-00372741.html |website=blastingnews |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://uk.blastingnews.com/showbiz-tv/2015/04/big-bang-the-kings-of-kpop-are-back-00372741.html |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Korea's boy band BigBang rule MTV TRL Awards |url=http://gulfnews.com/life-style/music/korea-s-boy-band-bigbang-rule-mtv-trl-awards-1.1019007 |website=Gulf News Music |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222230130/http://gulfnews.com/life-style/music/korea-s-boy-band-bigbang-rule-mtv-trl-awards-1.1019007 |archivedate=2015-12-22 }}</ref>，其中，G-Dragon更為團體贏得音樂界的尊敬與讚賞<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.nate.com/view/20100806n06154 |title='음악평론가' 임진모, "작곡하는 빅뱅은 아이돌 아니다" |publisher=Nate |date=2010-08-06 |accessdate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，而自[[Gaon音樂榜|加翁音樂榜]]開始追蹤銷量起，包括成員個人發行的曲目，BIGBANG已售出超過1億5千700萬張的唱片<ref>{{cite web|title=30 Mind Blowing Facts Every Fan Should Know About Kpop Group Big Bang |url=http://www.boomsbeat.com/articles/258760/20170422/30-mind-blowing-facts-fan-know-big-bang.htm |website=boomsbeat |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713002656/http://www.boomsbeat.com/articles/258760/20170422/30-mind-blowing-facts-fan-know-big-bang.htm |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，加上先前韓國音樂產業協會（MIAK）、韓國音樂內容產業協會（KMCIA）發行的銷量以及國家銷量已突破1億8千1百萬張，而在韓國、[[日本|日本]]及亞洲其他地區的數位單曲擁有超過1億2千8百萬張的銷量<ref name="總銷量">{{cite web|title=‘Kiss My Airs’ and 100,000 USD donations |url=https://theclassiclifesite.wordpress.com/2017/03/27/kiss-my-airs-and-100000-usd-donations-kpops-g-dragon-spreads-the-gift-of-giving-to-his-fans/ |website=The Classical Life |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717073544/https://theclassiclifesite.wordpress.com/2017/03/27/kiss-my-airs-and-100000-usd-donations-kpops-g-dragon-spreads-the-gift-of-giving-to-his-fans/ |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，平均每首主打歌下載量為430萬，非主打歌下載量為150萬，專輯銷量則超過1300萬張，這使其成為亞洲史上數位專輯最熱賣的團體{{r|總銷量}}<ref name="records">{{cite web |title=K-Pop Superstars BigBang Go Camping in YouTube Red’s First Korean Show |url=http://variety.com/2017/digital/news/bigbang-kpop-youtube-red-reality-show-1202399581/ |website=variety |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519222008/http://variety.com/2017/digital/news/bigbang-kpop-youtube-red-reality-show-1202399581/ |archivedate=2017-05-19 }}</ref>，也是[[男子音乐组合#全球暢銷男子音樂組合|世界上暢銷的男子音樂組合]]之一。<ref>{{cite web |title=‘Good Fight’ Heads To India, Nordics; Alexia Edwards Joins Expectation – Global Briefs |url=http://deadline.com/2017/04/imcx-pacts-with-india-pvr-the-good-fight-offshore-deals-expectation-hires-alexia-edwards-coo-cannes-marche-du-film-youtube-korean-boy-band-big-bang-1202078310/ |website=deadline |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625154717/http://deadline.com/2017/04/imcx-pacts-with-india-pvr-the-good-fight-offshore-deals-expectation-hires-alexia-edwards-coo-cannes-marche-du-film-youtube-korean-boy-band-big-bang-1202078310/ |archivedate=2017-06-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Rapper T.O.P from K-pop group Big Bang found unconscious after drug overdose |url=http://www.straight.com/blogra/921371/rapper-top-k-pop-group-big-bang-found-unconscious-after-drug-overdose |website=straight |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170611024253/http://www.straight.com/blogra/921371/rapper-top-k-pop-group-big-bang-found-unconscious-after-drug-overdose |archivedate=2017-06-11 }}</ref>

縱觀BIGBANG的職業生涯，他們已多次在[[BIGBANG獲獎及提名列表|韓國及國際各大頒獎典禮與各項排行榜獲得殊榮]]，包括「{{link-en|Cyworld Digital Music Awards|Cyworld Digital Music Awards|Cyworld數位音樂大賞}}」最暢銷的藝人<ref>{{cite web |title=[NEWS] Big Bang is #1 in Cyworld Hall of Fame! |url=http://www.dkpopnews.net/2011/03/news-big-bang-is-1-in-cyworld-hall-of.html |website=dkpopnews |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220141213/http://www.dkpopnews.net/2011/03/news-big-bang-is-1-in-cyworld-hall-of.html |archivedate=2016-12-20 }}</ref>、於「Mnet亞洲音樂大獎」獲得最多大獎的紀錄為依據被列入2018年[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]的偶像團體<ref>{{cite web|title=BIGBANG、EXO《MAMA》拿獎拿到進金氏紀錄 |url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2179836 |website=自由時報 |accessdate=2017-09-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901002243/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2179836 |archivedate=2017-09-01 }}</ref>，他們也是第一個進入「[[富比士百大名人|富比士百大名人]]」<ref>{{cite web |title=Bigbang |url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/bigbang/ |website=forbes |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517005725/https://www.forbes.com/profile/bigbang/ |archivedate=2017-05-17 }}</ref>、「福布斯30位30歲以下精英榜」音樂榜單名單的韓國歌手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.yg-life.com/archives/84796?lang=en#qtranslate-2-chooser |title=BIGBANG is listed in American Forbes' 「30 Under 30 Music: Gallant, Bigbang, Daya, Logic And The Class Of 2017」 |publisher=yg-life |date=2017-01-04 |accessdate=2017-01-04 }}</ref>，並以年收入高達4400萬美元位列「[[福布斯30位30歲以下精英榜|福布斯30位30歲以下精英榜]]」第13名的南韓唯一入榜者<ref name="auto">{{cite web |title=BIGBANG入選富比世30歲以下收入前30 |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161118002658-260404 |website=中時電子報 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104164248/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161118002658-260404 |archivedate=2017-01-04 }}</ref>。鑒於他們的全球知名度以及在韓國流行音樂的貢獻，《[[华盛顿邮报|華盛頓郵報]]》將他們描述為「亞洲最頂級的音樂團體」<ref name=":7">{{cite web |title=They’re the biggest band in Asia, but Big Bang’s days may be numbered |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/theyre-the-biggest-band-in-asia-but-big-bangs-days-may-be-numbered/2016/03/03/c267981c-8b02-4827-90c5-9968abbdc9ba_story.html?utm_term=.a6e47f7d626d |website=華盛頓郵報 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611005120/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/theyre-the-biggest-band-in-asia-but-big-bangs-days-may-be-numbered/2016/03/03/c267981c-8b02-4827-90c5-9968abbdc9ba_story.html |archivedate=2016-06-11 }}</ref>，而《[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]》、《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]》則形容他們為「全球最具影響力的男子組合」<ref name=":5">{{cite web |title=Big Bang's Global Influence: How to Build a Boy Band That Lasts |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/big-bangs-global-influence-how-835839 |website=好萊塢報導 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530121557/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/big-bangs-global-influence-how-835839 |archivedate=2016-05-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.yg-life.com/archives/73069?lang=en#qtranslate-2-chooser |title=BIGBANG&CL Nominated to be on the 2016 TIME 100 |language= |publisher=yg-life |date=2016-03-24 |accessdate=2017-01-03 }}</ref>，深獲國際肯定。

== 發展歷程 ==
=== 2000年－2006年：成立及早期活動 ===
在正式出道前，G-Dragon及太陽早於12歲時便被YG娛樂的社長[[梁玄錫|梁玄錫]]選中加入公司當練習生，T.O.P先前則是以藝名「Tempo」做為地下饒舌歌手<ref name="Crazy for K-Pop">{{cite web|archivedate=2009-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090726124034/http://showbizandstyle.inquirer.net/lifestyle/lifestyle/view/20090724-217073/Crazy-for-K-Pop |title=Crazy for K-Pop |publisher=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=2009-07-24 |url=http://showbizandstyle.inquirer.net/lifestyle/lifestyle/view/20090724-217073/Crazy-for-K-Pop |accessdate=2010-02-01 |last=Sablan |first=Niño Mark |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，他最著名的歌曲是與NBK Gray一起合唱的〈Buckwild〉<ref>{{cite web|title=HOW CHOI SEUNGHYUN BECAME T.O.P |url=https://topoppa.wordpress.com/2012/07/10/how-choi-seunghyun-became-t-o-p/ |website=topoppa |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503065648/https://topoppa.wordpress.com/2012/07/10/how-choi-seunghyun-became-t-o-p/ |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>。在YG娛樂將G-Dragon視為組建男團的候選人後，G-Dragon聯繫了兒時的好友T.O.P，讓他參加面試<ref>{{cite web|title=[新스타고백]지드래곤⑤아이돌그룹 활동, 망설였다 |url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010012610365249416 |website=archive |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406032928/http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010012610365249416 |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>，大聲及勝利則是通過YG娛樂主辦的選秀，合格後成為該娛樂公司旗下的練習生。<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG剛出道竟然被笑長這樣！還被網友毒舌：你們在家都不照鏡子的嗎？ |url=http://www.ebcbuzz.com:80/watch/23744 |website=ebcbuzz |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211194950/http://www.ebcbuzz.com/watch/23744 |archivedate=2016-02-11 }}</ref>

2006年7月，YG娛樂透過十一集的記錄片《BIGBANG出道實錄》敘述BIGBANG的出道經過。隊長兼饒舌的G-Dragon和主唱太陽因已經練習了6年之久，均有著深厚的實力並已訂定簽約。領唱姜大聲在選拔過程得到多位老師的好評；勝利與[[張賢勝|張賢勝]] （後曾任[[BEAST|BEAST]]成員）在選拔中落敗。而在落敗後獲得重選機會時，勝利最後獲勝加入BIGBANG，賢勝而淘汰，並離開公司<ref>{{cite web |title=BIOGRAPHY OF BIG BANG~KOREAN BOYBAND |url=http://www.ib-article.com/2012/08/biography-of-big-bang-korean-boyband.html |website=.ib-article |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122020929/http://www.ib-article.com/2012/08/biography-of-big-bang-korean-boyband.html |archivedate=2017-01-22 }}</ref>。此記錄片在播出後便受到廣大關注，在網上的收看次數達到160萬人次。<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG出道实录 开启偶像组合的新纪元 |url=http://www.sohu.com/a/37176567_148329 |website=搜狐 |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701022051/http://www.sohu.com/a/37176567_148329 |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>

2006年8月19日，在YG娛樂全力打造下，BIGBANG在韓國首爾奧林匹克競技場舉行的「YG Family 10週年演唱會」上正式出道，並在隔月公開播放<ref name="올 최고 기대주 빅뱅, 9월 중순부터 본격 활동 개시">{{cite web|script-title=ko:올 최고 기대주 빅뱅, 9월 중순부터 본격 활동 개시 |author= |publisher=Sports Chosun |date=2006-08-21 |url=http://sports.chosun.com/news/news_o.htm?name=/news/entertainment/200608/20060822/68v77108.htm |accessdate=2010-01-15 |language= |archivedate=2011-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708150000/http://sports.chosun.com/news/news_o.htm?name=%2Fnews%2Fentertainment%2F200608%2F20060822%2F68v77108.htm |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。不久之後於8月29日發行首張單曲專輯《BIGBANG》，包含〈A Fool's Only Tears〉、〈This Love〉以及[[朴春|朴春]]參與客串的〈We Belong Together〉，其中〈This Love〉改編自美國搖滾樂隊[[魔力紅|魔力紅]]的歌曲〈{{link-en|烈愛 (魔力紅歌曲)|This Love (Maroon 5 song)|烈愛}}〉，由G-Dragon改寫並演唱<ref name="BigBang1">{{cite web|title=Big Bang Profile |author= |publisher=KBS World |date= |url=http://world.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_artists_detail.htm?No=103896 |accessdate=2010-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201170812/http://world.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_artists_detail.htm?No=103896 |archivedate=2010-12-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang Profile on KBS |author= |publisher=KBS World |year=2007 |url=http://world.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_artists_detail.htm?No=103896 |accessdate=2010-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605093255/http://world.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_artists_detail.htm?No=103896 |archivedate=2010-06-05 |df= }}</ref>，此張單曲銷售近4萬張{{r|2007年專輯銷售量}}。第二張單曲專輯是在9月份發行的《BIGBANG Is V.I.P》，最終賣出了3萬2千張{{r|2007年專輯銷售量}}。同年12月21日，BIGBANG發佈首張正規專輯《[[BIGBANG_Vol.1_(BIGBANG專輯)|BIGBANG Vol.1]]》，並在12月舉辦出道後的第一場演唱會「The Real」<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG 2006 1st Concert 《The Real》首場演唱會 票價/座位圖/周邊商品 |url=http://yinghuapaocai.blogspot.tw/2006/11/bigbang-2006-1st-concert-the-real-information.html |website=YHPC櫻花泡菜 |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701022403/http://yinghuapaocai.blogspot.tw/2006/11/bigbang-2006-1st-concert-the-real-information.html |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>。截至2007年2月底，《BIGBANG Vol.1》已售出4萬8千張。{{r|2007年專輯銷售量}}

=== 2007年－2008年：進軍日本 ===
[[File:Big_Bang_In_Thailand.JPG|thumb]]
2007年2月8日，BIGBANG發行了他們在2006年12月30日舉行首次公演的演唱會專輯《[[The_Real_Vol.1_Live_Concert|The Real Vol.1現場音樂會]]》，到年底一共銷售超過1萬5千張<ref name="2007 Year-end Album Sales">{{cite web|title=2007 Year-end Album Sales |url=http://www.miak.or.kr/stat/kpop_2007_2.htm |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080508152311/http://www.miak.or.kr/stat/kpop_2007_2.htm |archivedate=2008-05-08 }}</ref>，而從5月27日起以[[仁川廣域市|仁川站]]為起點開始進行「{{link-ko|Want You巡迴演唱會|Want You Tour|Want You}}」巡迴演唱會以宣傳首張正規專輯《BIGBANG Vol.1》，期間共途徑五座城市，包括[[大邱廣域市|大邱]]、[[昌原市|昌原]]、[[全州市|全州]]及[[釜山廣域市|釜山]]。<ref name="How to Crack Japan: The Big Bang Theory">{{cite web |title=How to Crack Japan: The Big Bang Theory |url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1933111,00.html |website=TIME |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307023615/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1933111%2C00.html |archivedate=2016-03-07 }}</ref>

2007年8月16日，推出首張迷你專輯《Always》，《Always》代表組合有了些微改變，儘管成員們先前均參與過作詞作曲，但現在更專注於音樂風格的創新，G-Dragon負責創作首張迷你專輯中的大部分歌曲，包括另他們逐漸打開知名度的〈謊言〉（韓語：거짓말）<ref name="ALWAYS/RELEASE">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222132458/http://www.hankyung.com/news/app/newsview.php?aid=2007081791017&sid=83&nid=105type%3D1&pkind=all |url=http://www.hankyung.com/news/app/newsview.php?aid=2007081791017&sid=83&nid=105type=1&pkind=all |title=빅뱅, ‘Always’ 선주문 3만장 괴력 |publisher=Hankyung News |archivedate=2015-12-22 |language= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，特別的是，此張專輯引入[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]，引起相當正面的回饋，而主打曲〈謊言〉發佈後獲得一眾好評，評論將這首歌描述為「一演轟動」<ref name="Firstmeeting">{{cite web|title=Big Bang's Showcase & First Fan Meeting |author= |publisher=Arirang |date= |url=http://www.arirang.co.kr/Tv2/Showbiz_OnLocation.asp?PROG_CODE=TVCR0112&OnAir_Date=2007-09-03&sys_lang=Eng |accessdate=2008-01-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210085854/http://www.arirang.co.kr/Tv2/Showbiz_OnLocation.asp?PROG_CODE=TVCR0112&OnAir_Date=2007-09-03&sys_lang=Eng |archivedate=2009-02-10 }}</ref>，成為他們最熱門的歌曲之一。<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang's Showcase & First Fan Meeting |url=http://www.arirang.co.kr/Tv2/Showbiz_OnLocation.asp?PROG_CODE=TVCR0112&OnAir_Date=2007-09-03&sys_lang=Eng |website=arirang |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614005701/http://www.arirang.co.kr/Tv2/Showbiz_OnLocation.asp?PROG_CODE=TVCR0112&OnAir_Date=2007-09-03&sys_lang=Eng |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>

2007年11月22日，BIGBANG趁勝追擊推出第二張迷你專輯《[[Hot_Issue_(BIGBANG迷你專輯)|Hot Issue]]》，主打曲〈{{tsl|en|Last Farewell (Big Bang song)|最後的問候 (BIGBANG歌曲)|最後的問候}}〉（韓語：마지막 인사）取得與先前一樣的成功，均登上各大榜單之首，包括在Juke-On排行榜上連續8週蟬聯冠軍<ref name="빅뱅 쥬크온차트 8주 연속 1위 기염, JOO도 2주만에 7위 진입">{{cite web|title=빅뱅 쥬크온차트 8주 연속 1위 기염, JOO도 2주만에 7위 진입 |author=Kim, Hyung Woo |publisher=Newsen |date=2008-01-21 |url=http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?news_uid=200034&code=100200 |accessdate=2008-02-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209235612/http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?news_uid=200034&code=100200 |archivedate=2008-02-09 |deadurl=yes |language= }}</ref>，並取得「Cyworld數位音樂大賞」12月份的人氣歌曲獎<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG |url=http://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K2e668 |website=kpopn |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://kpopn.niusnews.com/%3DK2e668 |archivedate=2015-07-03 }}</ref>。為了答謝歌迷的支持，BIGBANG於12月28日至31日舉行為期3天「The Great」演唱會，而所有門票在開賣後僅10分鐘即銷售一空<ref name="Soldout">{{cite web|title=빅뱅, 단독콘서트 티켓 또 10분만에 매진 |url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2007112011064574626&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |website=StarNews |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2007112011064574626&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref><ref name="Soldout2">{{cite web|title=빅뱅 단독콘서트 티켓 5천석 10분 만에 매진 |url=http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=200711201110031002 |website=newsen |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622135252/http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=200711201110031002 |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>。然而，由於組合過度的演出，在成員均因過於疲勞不得不休養而暫停所有宣傳活動<ref name="Hospitalize">{{cite web |title=빅뱅, 멤버들 줄부상에 일시 활동중단 |url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2007123109144603151&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |website=StarNews |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701042927/http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2007123109144603151&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>，儘管如此，他們的專輯及單曲依然熱賣，讓唱片公司再次出版包裝二次發行<ref name="Big Bang's Albums in Short Supply">{{cite web|title=Big Bang's Albums in Short Supply |author= |publisher=KBS World |date=2007-12-26 |url=http://rki.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_chart_detail.htm?No=6858 |accessdate=2008-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081226141300/http://rki.kbs.co.kr/english/entertainment/enter_chart_detail.htm?No=6858 |archivedate=2008-12-26 |df= }}</ref>，憑藉著迷你專輯的成功，BIGBANG於年底橫掃韓國大型頒獎典禮各大獎項，當中包括在第9屆「Mnet亞洲音樂大獎」獲得最佳男子組合以及年度歌曲兩座大獎<ref>{{cite web|title=빅뱅 '올해의 노래'-슈주 '올해의 가수'…MKMF '아이돌 천하'(종합) |url=http://www.mydaily.co.kr/news/read.html?newsid=200711172254431132&ext=na |website=mydaily |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310165831/http://www.mydaily.co.kr/news/read.html?newsid=200711172254431132&ext=na |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>，其後，他們亦在第17屆「[[首爾音樂獎|首爾音樂賞]]」奪下大賞獎<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang Wins Pop Music Award |url=http://english.kbs.co.kr/entertainment/news/1505226_11858.html |website=KBS Global |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207174904/http://english.kbs.co.kr/entertainment/news/1505226_11858.html |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>，而根據相關報導，團體至年末一共收入高達120億韓元（約1150萬美元）。<ref name="빅뱅 올 360억원 대박 쳤다">{{cite web|script-title=ko:빅뱅 올 360억원 대박 쳤다 |author= |publisher=Nate |date=2008-09-11 |url=http://ask.nate.com/knote/view.html?num=1229021 |accessdate=2010-01-22 |language= |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2011-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009163942/http://ask.nate.com/knote/view.html?num=1229021 }}</ref>

