2007年年末，所屬經紀公司YG娛樂宣佈旗下男子組合BIGBANG將進軍日本，並在2008年1月4日發行首張日語迷你專輯《[[For_the_World|For the World]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=빅뱅 일본진출 멤버 이름 바꿔 활동 |url=http://isplus.live.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=3001571&cloc= |website=IS Plus |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401071652/http://isplus.live.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=3001571&cloc= |archivedate=2012-04-01 }}</ref>，僅靠著小幅宣傳就在日本最具影響力的排行榜[[Oricon公信榜|公信榜]]排名第十位<ref name="Big Bang, Oricon Chart">{{cite web| title = 빅뱅, '오리콘 차트' 이름 올리다 (Big Bang, putting their name up on 'Oricon Chart')| author =Kim, Sung Win | publisher =Hankooki | date =2008-02-14 |url =http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/music/200802/sp2008021407561495510.htm | accessdate = 2008-02-15| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080219200025/http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/music/200802/sp2008021407561495510.htm| archivedate= 2008-02-19 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no|language=}}</ref>，並在[[東京巨蛋城|東京巨蛋城]]內的[[MEETS_PORT|JCB Hall]]舉辦首場海外演唱會<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang FIRST solo concert at Tokyo Dome City’s JCB Hall in Japan |url=https://lovme2.wordpress.com/2008/03/11/big-bang-first-solo-concert-at-tokyo-dome-city%E2%80%99s-jcb-hall-in-japan/ |website=KPOP JPOP ENTERTAINMENT |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122100734/http://lovme2.wordpress.com/2008/03/11/big-bang-first-solo-concert-at-tokyo-dome-city%E2%80%99s-jcb-hall-in-japan/ |archivedate=2009-01-22 }}</ref>。結束在日本的宣傳後，BIGBANG回到韓國，雖然團體的活動因個人活動而推遲，但還是發行了第三張韓語迷你專輯《[[Stand_Up_(BIGBANG迷你專輯)|Stand Up]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=E&ATYPE=2&ARTIDX=3&Page=5&IDX=382|title=3rd Mini Album : Stand Up|publisher=YG Entertainment|accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>。此次作品與{{link-en|Daishi Dance|Daishi Dance}}及韓國搖滾樂團{{link-en|No Brain|No Brain}}進行合作，於發行後再度創下佳績，不僅唱片銷售突破20萬張<ref>{{cite web|url=http://miak.or.kr/stat/kpop_200809.htm |publisher=miak.or.kr |language= |script-title=ko:2008년 9월 가요순위건 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123024448/http://miak.or.kr/stat/kpop_200809.htm |archivedate=2009-01-23 |accessdate=2012-01-06 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>，其中主打曲〈{{link-en|一天一天 (BIGBANG歌曲)|Day by Day (Big Bang song)|一天一天}}〉（韓語：하루하루）均佔據多個數位音樂網站榜單首位，並蟬聯共六週的冠軍<ref name="Modellingcontract">{{cite web|title=Big Bang Signs Modeling Contract with FILA Korea |author= |publisher=KBS Global |date=2008-09-08 |url=http://english.kbs.co.kr/mcontents/entertainment/1546222_11692.html |accessdate=2011-02-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924063830/http://english.kbs.co.kr/mcontents/entertainment/1546222_11692.html |archivedate=2008-09-24 |df= }}</ref>，此外，〈一天一天〉也成為韓國最暢銷的單曲之一，僅在韓國就有超過540萬的下載量<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://onehallyu.com/topic/3909-%25E2%2599%2595-bigbang-sales-thread-160828-with-gaon400-108mln-digital-664mln-physical-73mln-tour-tickets-33bln-youtube-views-%25E2%2599%2595/|title=~♕ BIGBANG Sales Thread (160828 with GAON400: 108mln digital, 6.64mln physical, 7.3mln Tour tickets, 3.3bln Youtube views) ♕~ - Charts and Sales|access-date=2016-09-11}}</ref>，而在《Stand Up》中也包含排名在第5位的〈天國〉、第10位的〈Oh My Friend〉以及第20位的〈A Good Man〉與〈Lady〉。<ref name="Othersongscharting">{{cite web|script-title=ko:빅뱅 정규2집 ‘리멤버’ 선주문 20만장 넘었다! 8일 본격 활동개시 |first=Park |last=Seoyoung |publisher=Newsen |date=2008-11-04 |url=http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?news_uid=271977 |accessdate=2010-01-15 |language= |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401141044/http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?news_uid=271977 }}</ref>

在準備下一張韓語作品期間，BIGBANG於2008年10月9日推出首張日語正規專輯《[[Number_1_(BIGBANG日語專輯)|Number 1]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=E&ATYPE=2&ARTIDX=3&Page=7&IDX=394|title=Japan 1st Album : Number 1|publisher=YG Entertainment|accessdate=2013-11-07}}</ref>，此張專輯躋身日本公信榜每日專輯排行榜中的第三名<ref>{{cite web|title=韓組合BigBang首張日本專輯打進公信榜前三甲 |url=http://ent.big5.enorth.com.cn/system/2008/10/23/003737625.shtml |website=北方網 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://ent.big5.enorth.com.cn/system/2008/10/23/003737625.shtml |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>。11月5日，發行第二張韓語正規專輯《[[Remember_(BIGBANG專輯)|Remember]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=2nd Album : Remember |url=http://www.ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=K&ATYPE=2&ARTIDX=3&Page=9&IDX=405 |website=YG娛樂 |accessdate=2017-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807072622/http://www.ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=K&ATYPE=2&ARTIDX=3&Page=9&IDX=405 |archivedate=2017-07-01 }}</ref>，收錄的主打曲〈紅霞〉（韓語：붉은노을）依舊在發表後空降韓國音樂榜單首位，專輯則賣出超過21萬張<ref name="Othersongscharting"/>，再度的成功，使BIGBANG於第10屆「Mnet亞洲音樂大獎」拿下成軍以來第二座最佳男子組合獎<ref name="2008 Mnet KM Music Festival">{{cite web| title = 2008 Mnet KM Music Festival | author =  | publisher =[[Mnet_Asian_Music_Awards|MKMF]] | date =2008-09-08 |url =http://mkmf.mnet.com/2008/Intro/Intro.asp | accessdate = 2010-01-15 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100202034431/http://mkmf.mnet.com/2008/Intro/Intro.asp <!--Added by H3llBot--> | archivedate =2010-02-02|language=}}</ref>。至2008年底，據報導BIGBANG的總收入為360億韓元（約3450萬美元）。<ref name="빅뱅 올 360억원 대박 쳤다"/>

=== 2009年－2010年：個人發展及子團誕生 ===
