雖然組合在2009年初處於休息的狀態，但成員也忙於個人活動，而在3月27日重聚後與當時被稱作「女版BIGBANG」的同公司新女團[[2NE1|2NE1]]進行合作並一同拍攝音樂錄影帶<ref name="Lollipopnumberone">{{cite web|title=빅뱅-2NE1 ‘롤리팝’ 엠넷차트 4주연속 1위 기염 |url=http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=200904281525541002 |website=newsen |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703011239/http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=200904281525541002 |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>，推出了用來宣傳[[LG集團|LG Cyon]]手機的單曲《{{link-en|Lollipop (BIGBANG與2NE1單曲)|Lollipop (Big Bang and 2NE1 song)|Lollipop}}》<ref name="2NE1 Picked Artist of the Year by Mnet">{{cite web|title=2NE1 Picked Artist of the Year by Mnet |url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/special/2009/12/178_57322.html |website=The Korea Times |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620091703/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/special/2009/12/178_57322.html |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>，另外BIGBANG也發行了第三張單曲〈So Fresh, So Cool〉以宣傳啤酒品牌「Hite」，然而勝利因還未達到可飲酒年齡，未參與其中<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang - So Fresh So Cool HITE CF |url=http://sengkakada.blogspot.tw/2009/04/big-bang-so-fresh-so-cool-hite-cf.html |website=blogspot |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703013550/http://sengkakada.blogspot.tw/2009/04/big-bang-so-fresh-so-cool-hite-cf.html |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>。8月19日，他們的日語正規專輯《[[BIGBANG_(2009年專輯)|BIGBANG]]》問世<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang Doing Well in Japan |url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/include/print.asp?newsIdx=50716 |website=koreatimes |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210214/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/include/print.asp?newsIdx=50716 |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>，由[[環球音樂_(日本)|日本環球音樂]]發行，在活動期間也同時宣傳了〈[[My_Heaven|My Heaven]]〉、〈[[Gara_Gara_GO!!|Gara Gara GO!!]]〉單曲<ref name="chosun online">{{cite web|title=BIGBANGの3rdシングルがオリコン3位 |url=http://www.chosunonline.com/entame/20091104000057 |website=chosunonline |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091107045313/http://www.chosunonline.com/entame/20091104000057 |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref><ref name="RBB">{{cite web |title=「おひとりさま」主題歌など人気急上昇BIGBANGの魅力をたっぷりと |url=https://www.rbbtoday.com/article/2009/11/06/63565.html |website=rbbtoday |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513085407/http://www.rbbtoday.com/article/2009/11/06/63565.html |archivedate=2016-05-13 }}</ref>，其中〈My Heaven〉是韓語迷你三輯《Stand Up》收錄曲〈天國〉（韓語：천국）的日語再錄版，〈My Heaven〉甫發行便登上日本公信榜第三名<ref>{{cite web |title=BigBang单曲韩日同步发行 首日登公信榜第三位 |url=http://korea.sohu.com/20090709/n265097340.shtml |website=搜狐 韓娛新聞 |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703020256/http://korea.sohu.com/20090709/n265097340.shtml |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>，〈Gara Gara GO!!〉則位居第五<ref>{{cite web |title=BigBang日本人气高 第二张单曲获公信榜第五名 |url=http://music.yule.sohu.com/20090812/n265894941.shtml |website=搜狐音樂 |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703020758/http://music.yule.sohu.com/20090812/n265894941.shtml |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>。回韓國後，成員專注於個人活動，包括T.O.P出演[[電視劇|電視劇]]《[[IRIS_(電視劇)|特務情人IRIS]]》飾演殺手的角色<ref>{{cite web |title=T.O.P俊秀包緊緊入伍　300粉相送「要健康回來」 |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170209/1052339/ |website=蘋果日報 |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209184352/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170209/1052339/ |archivedate=2017-02-09 }}</ref>，太陽則分別於10月15日及11月13日推出個人單曲〈Where U At?〉及〈Wedding Dress〉<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang members to continue solo career |url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20090928000083 |website=The Korea Herald |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111163424/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20090928000083 |archivedate=2013-11-11 }}</ref>，而在成員於各自的領域活動下，同時也重聚為日劇《[[單身情歌|單身情歌]]》錄製主題曲〈[[让我听你的声音|讓我聽你的聲音]]〉。<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang does “Ohitorisama” opening |url=http://www.tokyograph.com/news/big-bang-does-ohitorisama-opening/ |website=tokyograph |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308152828/http://www.tokyograph.com/news/big-bang-does-ohitorisama-opening/ |archivedate=2016-03-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang Will Sing Opening Theme for Japanese Drama |url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/special/2009/11/178_53692.html |website=koreatimes |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620080952/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/special/2009/11/178_53692.html |archivedate=2017-06-20 }}</ref>

