1&aid=210021800168&t= | archivedate =2012-12-05 }}</ref>。6月9日，推出第四張日文單曲《[[Tell_Me_Goodbye|Tell Me Goodbye]]》，此曲是韓劇《IRIS》的日語再發行版本<ref name="TMG/IRIS">{{cite web|title=유인나, 한솥밥 YG 빅뱅 뮤비 ‘텔미 굿바이’ 출연 |author= |publisher=Joins |date=2010-05-20 |url=http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=4184887&ctg=15 |accessdate=2010-05-20 |language= |archivedate=2013-06-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621040831/http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=4184887&ctg=15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，公開後不僅大受好評<ref name="TMG/IRIS" />，並在第52屆「[[日本唱片大獎|日本唱片大賞]]」獲得年度歌曲獎<ref name="Honor">{{cite web|title=Big Bang to receive honor at Japan Record Awards |author=Hong, Lucia |publisher=10asiae |date=2010-11-22 |url=http://10.asiae.co.kr/Articles/new_view.htm?sec=ent0&a_id=2010112211113414254 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126144842/http://10.asiae.co.kr/Articles/new_view.htm?sec=ent0&a_id=2010112211113414254 |archivedate=2010-11-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，此外，為了「[[2010年世界盃足球賽|2010年世界盃足球賽]]」，BIGBANG另外發表有韓國搖滾樂團Transfixion與[[花式滑冰|花式滑冰]][[运动员|運動員]][[金妍兒|金妍兒]]參與客串的歌曲〈Shout of the Reds〉<ref name="KIMYUNA/SHOUTOFTHEREDS">{{cite web | script-title =ko:빅뱅-김연아-트랜스픽션 월드컵 응원가 ‘승리의 함성’ 공개 | author =Cho, Sangwon | publisher =KW News | date =2010-05-16 | url =http://www.kwnews.co.kr/nview.asp?s=801&aid=210051500015&t= | accessdate =2010-05-20 | language = | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://archive.is/20121208182634/http://www.kwnews.co.kr/nview.asp?s=801&aid=210051500015&t= | archivedate =2012-12-08 }}</ref>。而在這一年中，大部分時間成員再次各自展開活動<ref name="탑, 빅뱅 단독공연서 솔로곡 깜짝 발표">{{cite web| script-title=ko:탑, 빅뱅 단독공연서 솔로곡 깜짝 발표 | author =Kim, Hyung Woo  | publisher =Star News | date =2010-01-21 |url =http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2010012109410130214&type=3 | accessdate = 2011-01-21|language=}}</ref>，成員T.O.P發行個人數位單曲〈Turn It Up〉參與電影《[[走進炮火中|走進炮火中]]》的演出<ref>{{cite web|title=Turn It Up (Digital Single) |url=http://www.ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=E&ATYPE=2&PTYPE=&ARTIDX=19&PROIDX=&IDX=81&page=1 |website=YG娛樂 |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208211045/http://www.ygfamily.com/artist/Album.asp?LANGDIV=E&ATYPE=2&PTYPE=&ARTIDX=19&PROIDX=&IDX=81&page=1 |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=T.O.P RUSHED TO THE HOSPITAL WHILE FILMING INTO THE FIRE [NEWS] |url=http://bigbangupdates.com:80/2010/05/top-rushed-to-hospital-while-filming.html |website=bigbangupdates |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018111157/http://bigbangupdates.com/2010/05/top-rushed-to-hospital-while-filming.html |archivedate=2016-10-18 }}</ref>、成員太陽發行個人首張正規專輯《{{link-en|Solar (太陽專輯)|Solar (Taeyang album)|Solar}}》以及子團體[[GD&TOP|GD&TOP]]的首次亮相<ref>{{cite web|title=SOLAR FLARE UP : BIG BANG’S < TAEYANG > SHINES BRIGHT ON BRAND NEW ‘INTERNATIONAL’ RELEASE |url=http://dfsb.kr/projects/solar-flare-up-big-bangs-taeyang-shines-bright-on-brand-new.html |website=DFSB |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304173442/http://dfsb.kr/projects/solar-flare-up-big-bangs-taeyang-shines-bright-on-brand-new.html |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang duo on TV today |url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2930881 |website=koreajoongangdaily |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310211417/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2930881 |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>，期間，BIGBANG獲頒幾個著名的獎項，包括在第24屆「[[日本金唱片大獎|日本金唱片大賞]]」獲得最佳五位藝人獎與最佳新人獎<ref name="24JGDA/newcomerwin">{{cite web| title = ビッグバン・東方神起、日本ゴールドディスク賞受賞 (Gods of the Rising East win Japanese Gold Disc Award) | author = | publisher =Japan Joins | date =2010-02-25 |url =http://japanese.joins.com/article/article.php?aid=126622&servcode=700&sectcode=720 | accessdate = 2010-02-25| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100301040450/http://japanese.joins.com/article/article.php?aid=126622&servcode=700&sectcode=720| archivedate= 2010-03-01 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no|language=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Korean boom hits the Japan Record Awards with Big Bang |url=https://japantoday.com/category/entertainment/korean-boom-hits-the-japan-record-awards-with-big-bang |website=japantoday |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703025257/https://japantoday.com/category/entertainment/korean-boom-hits-the-japan-record-awards-with-big-bang |archivedate=2017-07-03 }}</ref>、「[[MTV日本音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV日本音樂錄影帶大獎]]」所頒的最佳流行音樂錄影帶及最佳新人獎。<ref>{{cite web |title=빅뱅'MTV 뮤직 어워드 재팬'3관왕 |url=http://www.incheonilbo.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=1644 |website=incheonilbo |accessdate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073243/http://www.incheonilbo.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=1644 |archivedate=2016-03-05 }}</ref>

