經過近兩年在韓國的團體空白期後，BIGBANG於2011年2月24日發行第四張迷你專輯《[[Tonight_(BIGBANG迷你專輯)|Tonight]]》，並在2月25日至27日「{{link-ko|Big Show 2011|BIG SHOW 2011}}」演唱會上首次表演<ref name="Comeback">{{cite web|title=Big Bang's Concert ''2011 Big Show'' To Be Held In February! |author=Kim, Sunny |publisher=MTV Korea |date=2010-12-06 |url=http://www.mtvk.com/2010/12/06/big-bangs-concert-2011-big-show-to-be-held-in-february/ |accessdate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210093910/http://www.mtvk.com/2010/12/06/big-bangs-concert-2011-big-show-to-be-held-in-february/ |archivedate=2010-12-10 |df= }}</ref><ref name="Comeback2">{{cite web| title = 컴백 빅뱅, 엠넷 ‘빅뱅TV 라이브’ 전격 방송 ‘6곡 최초 공개’ | author =Lee, Soo-yeon  | publisher =Newsen | date =2011-02-26 |url =http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=201102260848121002&search=title&searchstring=%EB%B9%85%EB%B1%85 | accessdate = 2011-02-27}}</ref>。《Tonight》在[[Cyworld|Cyworld]]的預售量近1萬張，打破[[東方神起|東方神起]]在2008年創下的6千5百張的記錄<ref>{{cite web|title=(NEWS) Big Bang sells 10,000 albums in pre-sales, doubles Seo Taiji and TVXQ’s records! |url=http://allbigbang.tumblr.com/post/3445343005/news-big-bang-sells-10000-albums-in-pre-sales |website=allbigbang |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709050414/http://allbigbang.tumblr.com/post/3445343005/news-big-bang-sells-10000-albums-in-pre-sales |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>，並且在一週內就上升至10萬張<ref>{{cite web|title=빅뱅, 오늘 음반판매 10만장 돌파..음원도 돌풍 |url=http://media.daum.net/entertain/newsview?cateid=1033&newsid=20110301090904462&p=poctan |website=OSEN |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117021141/http://media.daum.net/entertain/newsview?cateid=1033&newsid=20110301090904462&p=poctan |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>，同時引起熱烈反響，韓國知名媒體《Asiae》稱讚他們音樂的新方向，認為在這兩年的空窗期中，團體的風格和音樂情感變得更加深刻<ref>{{cite web|title='더빅뱅쇼' 빅뱅, 2년 3개월만에 공중파 첫 선··'강렬+파격' |url=http://asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2011022801462334134&sec=ent1 |website=asiae |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305215648/http://asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2011022801462334134&sec=ent1 |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>。而據媒體報導，專輯所產生的收入高達70億韓元（約660萬美元）<ref>{{cite web |title='첫방도 안한' 빅뱅, 컴백 6일만에 매출 '70억' |url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2011030210355042601&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |website=Star News |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709051148/http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2011030210355042601&outlink=1&ref=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>，其後，同名主打曲登上[[2011年Gaon單曲冠軍作品列表|加翁數位單曲榜週榜]]冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=2011년 11주차 Digital Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=11&hitYear=2011&termGbn=week |website=Gaon |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805121029/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=11&hitYear=2011&termGbn=week |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>

2011年4月8日，BIGBANG推出《Tonight》特別版專輯，主打歌為〈Love Song〉及〈Stupid Liar〉<ref>{{cite web |title=빅뱅 1년간 대표곡이 한곳에… 'SPECIAL EDITION' 앨범 공개! |url=http://www.ajunews.com/common/redirect.jsp?newsId=20110403000191 |website=아주경제 |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709053258/http://www.ajunews.com/common/redirect.jsp?newsId=20110403000191 |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>，亦包括各成員在2010年及2011年的Solo曲目〈I Need A Girl〉、〈High High〉、〈怎麼辦〉及大聲在此張專輯的個人獨唱單曲〈Baby Don't Cry〉<ref>{{cite web|title=BIGBANG (Special Edition) |url=https://itunes.apple.com/tw/album/bigbang-special-edition/id441435544?l=en |website=iTunes |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709053729/https://itunes.apple.com/tw/album/bigbang-special-edition/id441435544?l=en |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>。4月16日，公開〈Love Song〉音樂錄影帶<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IKZEmLvYVF0|title=BIGBANG - LOVE SONG M/V|accessdate=2017-07-09|work=[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}</ref>。拍攝當中，YG娛樂耗資20萬美元引進韓國業界從未使用的四面攝影機（4 point wire camera）<ref>{{cite web |title=BB 新 MV 耗資20萬美金 |url=http://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K0omol9 |website=kpopn |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704142916/http://kpopn.niusnews.com/%3DK0omol9 |archivedate=2016-07-04 }}</ref>，而音樂錄影帶發布後僅兩天的時間在[[Youtube|Youtube]]官方頻道的點閱率已突破200萬觀看人次。<ref name="LoveSong">{{cite web| title =빅뱅 '러브송' MV, 전세계 유튜브 점령…이틀만에 100만 클릭 (Big Bang's ‘LOVE SONG’ M/V over two million views in two days) | author = Lee, Eunji| publisher =My Daily | date =2011-04-16 |url =http://www.mydaily.co.kr/news/read.html?newsid=201104161203371114|  accessdate = 2011-04-16| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110515162543/http://www.mydaily.co.kr/news/read.html?newsid=201104161203371114| archivedate= 2011-05-15 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no|language=}}</ref>

2011年11月6日，BIGBANG以超過5千8百萬的票數成為「[[2011年MTV歐洲音樂大獎|MTV歐洲音樂大獎]]」亞洲太平洋地區代表並成功奪下最佳世界藝人獎，使他們成為歷史上第一個獲頒此項大獎的亞洲歌手<ref name="guardian">{{cite web|title=Bored by Cowell pop? Try K-pop |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/dec/15/cowell-pop-k-pop |website=theguardian |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708165642/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/dec/15/cowell-pop-k-pop |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>。而後BIGBANG參加「2011 YG Family巡迴演唱會」以慶祝YG娛樂成立十五週年<ref>{{cite web |title=大聲、GD：想念音樂和舞台 |url=http://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K2c7e570 |website=kpopn |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709060259/http://kpopn.niusnews.com/%3DK2c7e570 |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>，接著在12月14日發行第三張精選輯《[[The_Best_of_Big_Bang_(BIGBANG日語精選輯)|The Best of BIGBANG]]》，專輯中包含熱門歌曲〈一天一天〉的日語版本<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG、DVD&ベスト盤発売延期 リーダー大麻問題で波紋広がる |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2002517/full/ |website=oricon |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208144023/http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2002517/full/ |archivedate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>，精選輯在發售的第一天以14,504張的銷售量空降公信榜專輯排行榜冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang最新日文專輯攻上公信榜1位 |url=http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/13704%3Ffb_comment_id%3D10150417199192031_19825337 |website=韓星網 |accessdate=2017-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709061238/http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/13704?fb_comment_id=10150417199192031_19825337#f2d670bf67ac064 |archivedate=2017-07-09 }}</ref>

=== 2012年－2014年：首次世界巡演 ===
[[File:BIGBANG_in_K-Collection_2012.jpg|thumb]]
2012年1月，所屬經紀公司YG娛樂開始發佈BIGBANG第五張韓語迷你專輯《Alive》相關預告，並宣佈將在2月29日正式發行數位及實體專輯<ref>{{cite web |title=BIGBANG Alive 預購開跑 |url=https://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K0188a82 |website=kpopn |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717044715/https://kpopn.niusnews.com/%3DK0188a82 |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，兩週內的預購數達到26萬張<ref>{{cite web|title=빅뱅 새앨범 선주문 26만장 |url=http://news.nate.com/view/20120228n02563?mid=e0102 |website=東亞體育 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117021141/http://news.nate.com/view/20120228n02563?mid=e0102 |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>。主打曲之一〈{{link-en|Blue (BIGBANG歌曲)|Blue (Big Bang song)|Blue}}〉在專輯發行前一週提前釋出，公開後旋即佔據主要榜單第一名的位置，並連續三週蟬聯[[2012年Gaon單曲冠軍作品列表|加翁數位單曲榜]]冠軍<ref>{{cite web|title=2012년 09주차 Digital Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=09&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |website=Gaon Chart |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=09&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2012년 10주차 Digital Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=10&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |website=Gaon Chart |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924052735/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=10&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2012년 11주차 Digital Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=11&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |website=Gaon Chart |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710162146/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=11&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，成為[[2012年Gaon單曲冠軍作品列表#月榜冠軍作品|2月份]]的冠軍得主<ref>{{cite web|title=2012년 02월 Digital Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?serviceGbn=ALL&termGbn=month&hitYear=2012&targetTime=02&nationGbn=T |website=Gaon Chart |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403125423/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?serviceGbn=ALL&termGbn=month&hitYear=2012&targetTime=02&nationGbn=T |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，與音源同時發佈的音樂錄影帶則在Youtube上發佈僅一週，觀看次數達千萬記錄，同時獲得近期最熱門影片「Recently Most Popular」和焦點影片「Trending」兩枚金牌<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang's 'Blue' MV draws 8 million views, wins 2 Youtube gold medals |url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/02/big-bangs-blue-mv-draws-8-million-views-wins-2-youtube-gold-medals |website=allkpop |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/02/big-bangs-blue-mv-draws-8-million-views-wins-2-youtube-gold-medals |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，而專輯正式推出後取得了商業性的成功，不僅銷售量突破21萬張<ref>{{cite web|title=2012년 02월 Album Chart |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=02&hitYear=2012&termGbn=month |website=Gaon Chart |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118094346/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=02&hitYear=2012&termGbn=month |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，更在美國著名榜單告示牌K-pop熱門100首中的前十名歌曲就包攬了五個位置<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang's 'Alive' and Well on Billboard's Social 50 Chart |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483606/big-bangs-alive-and-well-on-billboards-social-50-chart |website=告示牌 |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483606/big-bangs-alive-and-well-on-billboards-social-50-chart |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，實體專輯則躋身告示牌200大專輯榜排行榜中的第150名，創下首位韓國藝人以韓語專輯進入此項排行榜<ref name="告示牌200大專輯榜"/><ref>{{cite web|title=K-Pop Hot 100: BIGBANG Is Unstoppable |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/502437/k-pop-hot-100-bigbang-is-unstoppable |website=告示牌 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211181238/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/502437/k-pop-hot-100-bigbang-is-unstoppable |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，BIGBANG的熱度也使他們在告示牌50強社交榜（Social 50）中排名第24位<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang makes an appearance on the Billboard Social 50 Chart |url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/04/big-bang-makes-an-appearance-on-the-billboard-social-50-chart |website=allkpop |accessdate=2017-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703081359/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/04/big-bang-makes-an-appearance-on-the-billboard-social-50-chart |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>，其後，亦獲得知名網站如《時代雜誌》的高度認可<ref name="How K-pop is">{{cite web|title=South Korea’s Greatest Export: How K-Pop’s Rocking the World |url=http://world.time.com/2012/03/07/south-koreas-greatest-export-how-k-pops-rocking-the-world/ |website=時代雜誌 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705051822/http://world.time.com/2012/03/07/south-koreas-greatest-export-how-k-pops-rocking-the-world/ |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>，並在3月15日登上美國[[格萊美|格萊美]]官方網頁，成為第一個被格萊美介紹的韓國歌手。<ref name="BigBang登美國格萊美網站首頁 K-POP熱潮令人嘆為觀止"/><ref>{{cite web |title=BB 登上葛萊美的首頁 |url=https://kpopn.niusnews.com/=K2sesj08 |website=kpopn |accessdate=2017-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717064503/https://kpopn.niusnews.com/%3DK2sesj08 |archivedate=2017-07-17 }}</ref>

[[File:Big_Bang_2012.jpg|thumb]]
2012年3月2日，BIGBANG在首爾奧林匹克公園體育館舉行為期三天，共吸引4萬名歌迷的週年演唱會「Big Show 2012」<ref name="Big Show 2012">{{cite web|title=Big Bang ‘Fantastic,’ Drove 40,000 Fans Wild |url=http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/5966/20120304/big-bang-big-bang-alive-tour-2012.htm |website=KpopStarz |accessdate=2017-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620213901/http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/5966/20120304/big-bang-big-bang-alive-tour-2012.htm |archivedate=2017-06-20 }}</ref>，正式拉開與[[Live_Nation_Entertainment|理想國演藝]]合作的首場世界巡演「{{link-en|Alive Galaxy世界巡迴演唱會|Big Bang Alive Galaxy Tour 2012|Alive Galaxy}}」帷幕<ref>{{cite web|title=Big Bang to hold 'ALIVE TOUR 2012' around the world through Live Nation! |url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/02/big-bang-to-hold-world-tour-through-live-nation/ |website=allkpop |accessdate=2017-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203215714/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2012/02/big-bang-to-hold-world-tour-through-live-nation/ |archivedate=2016-02-03 }}</ref>，這場「Big Show」演出也透過MTV World Stage在160個國家播放，促進他們世界巡演的宣傳<ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang to Appear on ‘MTV World Stage’ |url=http://mwave.interest.me/en/kpop-news/article/5626/big-bang-for-mtv-world-stage |website=Mwave |accessdate=2017-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729032148/http://mwave.interest.me/en/kpop-news/article/5626/big-bang-for-mtv-world-stage |archivedate=2017-07-29 }}</ref>，而為了即將到來的巡迴演唱會，YG娛樂邀請了曾與[[義大利裔美國人|義大利裔美國歌手]][[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]攜手合作「{{link-en|惡魔舞會世界巡迴演唱會|The Monster Ball Tour|惡魔舞會}}」巡演的著名編舞家{{link-en|勞瑞安·吉布森|Laurieann Gibson}}擔任指導，這意味著觀眾更加期待BIGBANG的舞臺表現<ref>{{cite web|title=BIG BANG PAIRS UP WITH LAURIEANN GIBSON |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2516200/big-bang-tour/ |website=MTV |accessdate=2017-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610180712/http://www.mtv.com/news/2516200/big-bang-tour/ |archivedate=2016-06-10 }}</ref>。團隊最終以2013年1月27日於首爾奧林匹克體操競技場作為「Alive Galaxy」為期近一年的終場演出，總計造訪12個國家24座城市，共48場演出，動員世界各地80萬名觀眾。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1kMojG4ij0|title=BIGBANG ALIVE 世界巡迴演唱會3DVD 精華版|date=2013-08-07|accessdate=2017-07-30|work=[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=빅뱅 월드투어…12개국·80만명·매출 800억 |url=http://m.mk.co.kr/index.php?year=2013&no=66641&TM=V1&PM=M0 |website=MK |accessdate=2017-07-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130207145934/http://m.mk.co.kr/index.php?year=2013&no=66641&TM=V1&PM=M0 |archivedate=2013-02-07 }}</ref>

