015年舉行的「MADE」世界巡迴演唱會成為在韓國歌手歷年所舉辦的巡演中規模最大的演唱會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3015485 |title=Big Bang returns home after epic world tour |language= |publisher=koreajoongangdaily |date=2016-03-01 |accessdate=2017-02-09 }}</ref>，並且成為史上瀏覽數最多的線上韓國流行音樂演唱會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1110182870|title=빅뱅, 월드투어 ‘MADE’ 中 텐센트 비디오 통해 생중계 (BIGBANG's World Tour "MADE" Live on China's Tencent)|last=|first=|date=2015-06-21|website=|publisher=Osen|access-date=|accessdate=2015-06-23}}</ref>。BIGBANG同時也是唯一一組在上海[[梅赛德斯-奔驰文化中心|梅賽德斯-奔馳文化中心]]連續舉行三場公演的外國歌手<ref name="Shanghai Concert">{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1110183415|title=Shanghai Concert of BIGBANG's World Tour Electrified 30,000 Fans… Great Success|last=|first=|date=2015-06-22|website=|publisher=Osen|access-date=|accessdate=2015-06-22}}</ref>，第一組在在[[马来西亚|馬來西亞]][[吉隆玻|吉隆玻]]舉辦兩天演唱會的韓國歌手<ref name="Malaysia Concert">{{cite web|url = http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/206014/20150531/bigbang-malaysia-2015-world-tour-made.htm|title = Big Bang Add Additional Date To MADE World Tour In Malaysia|publisher = kpopstarz.com|date = 2015-05-31|accessdate = 2015-06-22}}</ref>，第一組在香港兩次共三場演出門票完售的外國藝人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scmp.com/magazines/48hrs/article/1803062/big-bang-gigs-sell-out-and-sandra-ngs-stage-debut-hot-ticket-too|title=Big Bang gigs sell out|last=|first=|date=2015-05-21|website=|publisher=South China Morning Post|access-date=|accessdate=2015-06-22}}</ref>，也成為韓國歌手在美國、[[加拿大|加拿大]]及中國所舉行的韓國流行音樂演唱會中規模最大的演出<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/6576209/bigbang-america-tour-2015|title = BIGBANG Announce Huge Arena Tour for America This Fall|work = Billboard|date = 2015-05-27|accessdate = 2015-06-22}}</ref><ref name="torontoconcert">{{cite web|url = http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/music/2015/09/26/k-pop-band-big-bang-doing-booming-business-in-toronto.html|title = K-pop band Big Bang doing booming business in Toronto|publisher = The Star|date = 2015-09-26|accessdate = 2015-09-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1110236379|title = 빅뱅, 韓가수 최다 中 11개도시-18만명 동원 투어 성료.."다시 올 것"|publisher = OSEN|accessdate = 2015-08-31}}</ref>，巡演帶來的記錄性影片《{{link-en|BIGBANG MADE|Big Bang Made|BIGBANG MADE}}》在韓國成為瀏覽數最多的音樂紀錄片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=076&aid=0002957812|title=빅뱅, 10주년 영화 '빅뱅 메이드'…해외 10개국 추가 개봉|publisher=Naver|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>。2016年，他們迎來出道第十週年，並在韓國首爾世界盃競技場舉行紀念演唱會「0.TO.10」，一共聚集6萬5千名觀眾進場觀賞，成為韓國史上動員最多觀眾的單場演出。<ref name="KoreaN">{{Cite web|title=BIGBANG stages biggest-ever concert|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2016/08/143_212384.html|website=The Korean Times|accessdate=2016-08-21}}</ref>
